Description of the App
The App is a beat maker tool. The users of the App may create their own music and modify the sound with the app features. You don’t have to register you to use the Drum Machine service. The Service is free for all users except some features, which are charged with a subscription plan.
Please, note that for a best experience, we recommend to use headphones or speakers.
